item.title: Sources: Minnesota Vikings To Unveil “Winter Whiteout” Alternate Uniforms On June 7
item.description: According to multiple sources, the Minnesota Vikings will unveil their new “Winter Whiteout” alternate uniforms this Friday.

item.title: Baseball Players Wearing #4 Patch Today for Lou Gehrig Day
item.description: Why are baseball players wearing a number 4 patch on their uniforms today?
